text: tame kahi do ke na to hum tamane evum kahum chum ke mari pase allahana khajana che ane na to hum adrsya (ni vato) janum chum ane na to hum tamane evum kahum chum ke hum pharisto chum, hum to phakata je mari pase vahi ave che tenum anusarana karum chum, tame kahi do ke sum andhalo ane jonaro banne samana ho'i sake che? To sum tame cintana nathi karata
